{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["ヒガンバナの恋\n\n<size=45>その四　味方と過去<\/size>",1]]},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"重桜・鉄血の交流パーティーにて","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_night","bgm":"story-2"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"あら、あなたは鉄血の……","actor":307010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"グラーフ・ツェッペリンだ。珍しいな。まさかお前がこんな行事に参加するとは。","dir":-1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_night","actor":407010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"気まぐれよ。…それに小さい子たちの面倒を見る役は必要だわ。あなたもそうではなくて？","actor":307010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"……否定はできんな。我がお前に基づいて設計されたがゆえか…力はともかく、こういうところは結構近いのかもしれん。","actor":407010,"dir":-1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"今度は一緒に戦えるわね。まあ、もうひとりの私と思ったら心強いわ。","actor":307010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"……そういえば、お前が「カミ」とやらではなく、こっちに付いたと聞いた時は結構驚いたな。","actor":407010,"dir":-1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"確かに、あの時指揮官様と出会ってなければ、私は「カミ」に付いていたはずよ？","actor":307010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"ミッドウェイ…たしか指揮官はお前とその海域で、かの大戦を繰り返していたな。","actor":407010,"dir":-1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"戦争を続けて、味方を傷つけて、ただただ忌むべき敵の「力」を手に入れるために「覚醒」の可能性のある存在を探り続ける……","actor":307010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"ううん、あの「カミ」に付く私……本物かどうかはともかく――可能性の一つに過ぎないわ。","actor":307010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"可能性…？","actor":407010,"dir":-1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"同じ鏡に映された違う形の私…同じ情報に基づいて彫刻され、心が生まれる存在が皆「可能性」なのよ。","actor":307010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"あなたがいつしか戦うかもしれない私は、所詮はただの「可能性」でしかないもの。そしてあなたと一緒にお酒を飲んでいる私も…","actor":307010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"指揮官様と出会ったおかげで、「セイレーン」から救われた「可能性」として……","actor":307010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"……ふん、その口振りからすると指揮官はまだ知らないようだな。","actor":407010,"dir":-1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"いつか全てを明かす日が来るわ。","actor":307010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"私たちの存在、「聖域」、「魂」、そして形を成さない「素体」も…","actor":307010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"そうか……世迷言を言わせてしまったな……","actor":407010,"dir":-1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"ふふ、私も少しお酒が回ってしまったのかしらね……","actor":307010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_night","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"パーティーの喧騒とは離れた所で、二人の会話が続く。","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_night"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"それでも、指揮官様が愛してくれることを信じているわ……うふふ……","actor":307010,"blackBg":true,"dir":1,"side":2}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"CHICHENG4","fadeOut":1.5}